{
  "stem": "13690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I stated, in that house, we were upstairs, four of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother-- may she rest in peace, my brother-- older one, myself, and my sister, the youngest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four people were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The condition in-- in that place was bearable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In a way, there was no heat, but we were covered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Food-- we were brought up by-- by Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Placzek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was sufficient, but it was very difficult in as far the hygienics are concerned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no canalization or any means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore, it's interesting to state that the human body-- whatever it's consuming, it's giving practically back the same amount.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, we received one pail of water, and another pail was used just for the disposals.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was only done at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I must say, quite a big devotion for a man to do that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everyday, he took down one pail of disposals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He made us very comfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, to be able to sit down on the pail, he even created a sitting board out of wood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother was telling us family stories, which, really, it's not the time and place to repeat, going back from fathers and forefathers about the heritage of our people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides, being that Eli was three years older, he was somehow, some way, giving me some kind of lessons or reading books-- of which I did not mention before, the town was quite culturally well established.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a library with cases of books which were never used, and they were burned by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Gentile family that we were in hiding collected a lot of books, which we, in turn, used them during our stay in the bunker.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- mainly, the main staple food was bread and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
